THE HIGHEST OF PROFILES.

474
00:33:56,217 --> 00:33:58,202
WE NEED TO FIND A WAY
TO DRAW ATTENTION TO YOU,

475
00:33:58,202 --> 00:34:01,939
AND YOUR NEW LOOK JUST
ISN'T CUTTING IT ANYMORE.

476
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:03,391
WE NEED AN ISSUE.

477
00:34:03,891 --> 00:34:05,243
AN ISSUE?
YES.

478
00:34:05,243 --> 00:34:08,096
WE NEED PEOPLE TO THINK
THAT YOU'RE PASSIONATE
ABOUT SOMETHING.

479
00:34:08,596 --> 00:34:10,515
I AM PASSIONATE ABOUT--
OTHER THAN BEING MAYOR.

480
00:34:10,515 --> 00:34:12,850
OH.
I'M SURE WE'LL COME UP
WITH SOMETHING.

481
00:34:12,850 --> 00:34:14,852
IT'S JUST AN ISSUE.
HOW HARD CAN IT BE?

482
00:34:14,852 --> 00:34:18,289
OKAY, ISSUES.
ISSUES, ISSUES, ISSUES.

483
00:34:18,790 --> 00:34:21,292
WELL, HELP ME OUT HERE.
WHAT ARE SOME ISSUES?

484
00:34:21,292 --> 00:34:23,394
WELL, THIS IS AMERICA.
THEY'RE ENDLESS.
THERE'S GUN CONTROL.

485
00:34:23,394 --> 00:34:24,345
AGAINST IT.

486
00:34:24,345 --> 00:34:25,780
PROSTITUTION.
FOR IT.

487
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:28,116
TEENAGE PREGNANCY.
OH, PLEASE!

488
00:34:28,116 --> 00:34:30,118
DON'T GET ME STARTED
ON TEENAGERS.
WHAT NOW?

489
00:34:30,118 --> 00:34:34,105
THERE'S ALL THESE FILES
INVOLVING DELINQUENT
TEENAGE CRAP.

490
00:34:34,105 --> 00:34:37,475
STATUTORY RAPE.
HE'S 18, SHE'S 15 AND PREGNANT.

491
00:34:37,475 --> 00:34:38,476
THIS COULD WORK.

492
00:34:38,476 --> 00:34:39,927
WHAT?
THIS IS PERFECT.

493
00:34:39,927 --> 00:34:43,347
SEX OFFENDERS.
I LOVE SEX OFFENDERS!

494
00:34:43,347 --> 00:34:45,349
YOU COULD BE
AGAINST THEM.
OKAY.

495
00:34:45,349 --> 00:34:47,752
ARE YOU SURE THIS IS AN ISSUE
PEOPLE REALLY CARE ABOUT?

496
00:34:48,252 --> 00:34:50,972
LYDIA,
THIS IS THE BIBLE BELT,
THEY'RE GONNA LOVE IT.

497
00:34:50,972 --> 00:34:53,224
OKAY.
[ Chuckles ]

498
00:34:53,224 --> 00:34:55,226
THIS ISN'T THE BIBLE BELT,
YOU MORON.

499
00:34:55,226 --> 00:34:58,029
BUT THEY
DON'T KNOW THAT.
NO, THEY DON'T.

500
00:34:58,429 --> 00:35:00,882
OH, I'M GONNA THROW THE BOOK
AT THIS KID.

501
00:35:00,882 --> 00:35:02,884
AH!
OH. YOUNG ADULT.

502
00:35:02,884 --> 00:35:04,886
THANK YOU.

503
00:35:06,370 --> 00:35:08,372
GUILTY.

504
00:35:08,372 --> 00:35:11,325
SAY IT. GUILTY!
GUILTY!

505
00:35:11,325 --> 00:35:13,778
[ Amber ]
WHILE LYDIA PLOTTED
THE YOUNG ADULT'S FUTURE,

506
00:35:13,778 --> 00:35:16,197
ADAM MET WITH
THE YOUTH PASTOR...

507
00:35:16,614 --> 00:35:20,218
TO WORK OUT
THE MORE IMPORTANT ISSUES
OF HIS NOW COMPLICATED LIFE.

508
00:35:20,218 --> 00:35:23,221
I KNOW WE CAN STILL DO IT,
AND IT WON'T GET
INTO THE BABY'S FACE,

509
00:35:23,221 --> 00:35:26,891
BUT I'M TRYING TO
FIGURE OUT WHAT TO DO FROM
A RELIGIOUS PERSPECTIVE.

510
00:35:34,699 --> 00:35:38,152
[ Amber ]
GINGER FINALLY HAD
SOME POSITIVE ROLE MODELS,

511
00:35:38,152 --> 00:35:39,654
NOT THAT IT HELPED.

512
00:35:40,154 --> 00:35:43,307
ARE YOU ON
FRIGGIN' CRACK?

513
00:35:43,307 --> 00:35:45,760
GINGER, HONEY,

514
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:48,162
WE DON'T USE
LANGUAGE LIKE THAT
AT THE DINNER TABLE.

515
00:35:48,162 --> 00:35:52,333
I DON'T LOVE YOU.
I LOVE JOHNNY.

516
00:35:52,333 --> 00:35:53,251
YEAH, I KNOW, OKAY?
I DON'T LOVE YOU EITHER.

517
00:35:53,751 --> 00:35:56,154
IT'S JUST A PERCEPTION THING
FOR ALL THE STUPID PEOPLE.

518
00:35:56,154 --> 00:35:57,588
CHUCK'S SURE
IT'LL GET ME OFF.

519
00:35:57,588 --> 00:36:00,858
BUT JOHNNY'S GETTING PAROLED
IN A COUPLE OF MONTHS.

520
00:36:00,858 --> 00:36:02,810
GINGER, ALL WE
HAVE TO DO IS LIE.

521
00:36:02,810 --> 00:36:06,164
WHOA!
LYING IS A SIN, ADAM.

522
00:36:06,164 --> 00:36:07,532
WE'RE EMBELLISHING.

523
00:36:07,532 --> 00:36:10,535
SO WHETHER YOU LOVE GINGER,
MARY ANN OR THE PROFESSOR,

524
00:36:10,535 --> 00:36:13,421
IT REALLY DOESN'T MATTER.

525
00:36:17,758 --> 00:36:20,761
HERE, HONEY, I KNOW
HOW MUCH YOU LIKE WIENERS.

526
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:24,398
WE'RE RUNNING
OUT OF OPTIONS, HERE.

527
00:36:24,398 --> 00:36:26,901
YOU GUYS AT LEAST
LIKE EACH OTHER, RIGHT?

528
00:36:26,901 --> 00:36:30,254
HMM.
I NEVER REALLY EVEN
THOUGHT ABOUT IT.

529
00:36:30,254 --> 00:36:33,040
I MEAN, HE JUST GIVES ME
REALLY GOOD BONE.

530
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,028
HONEY?

531
00:36:44,852 --> 00:36:46,854
[ Knock On Door ]

532
00:36:46,854 --> 00:36:48,356
YEAH?

533
00:36:55,429 --> 00:36:57,381
YOU KNOW, SON, I...

534
00:36:59,317 --> 00:37:03,221
I FEEL PARTIALLY RESPONSIBLE
FOR WHAT'S HAPPENED.

535
00:37:03,221 --> 00:37:05,573
COOL. THANKS, DAD.

536
00:37:05,573 --> 00:37:10,294
IT'S OBVIOUS YOU KNOW ALL ABOUT
THE BIRDS AND THE BEES, HUH?

537
00:37:10,294 --> 00:37:14,298
YEAH.
[ Snickering ]

538
00:37:14,298 --> 00:37:17,802
BUT THERE ARE...

539
00:37:17,802 --> 00:37:19,303
ALTERNATIVES.

540
00:37:19,804 --> 00:37:21,722
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

541
00:37:23,107 --> 00:37:25,159
IT'S CALLED...

542
00:37:25,159 --> 00:37:26,460
MASTURBATING.

543
00:37:27,812 --> 00:37:28,813
DAD...

544
00:37:28,813 --> 00:37:31,282
IT'S NOTHING TO BE
EMBARRASSED ABOUT, SON.

545
00:37:31,282 --> 00:37:33,734
COME ON.
I'LL SHOW YOU HOW.

546
00:37:33,734 --> 00:37:35,686
I DIDN'T GET THESE CALLUSES
WORKING IN THE GARDEN.

547
00:37:36,187 --> 00:37:38,689
COME ON.
WE'LL DO IT TOGETHER.
DAD, I ALREADY KNOW HOW.

548
00:37:38,689 --> 00:37:40,658
THEN WHY AREN'T YOU DOING IT?

549
00:37:40,658 --> 00:37:43,110
I DO.

550
00:37:43,110 --> 00:37:46,030
WELL, THEN WHY AREN'T YOU
DOING IT MORE OFTEN?

551
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:48,699
WHENEVER YOU GET THE URGE,
JUST POLITELY EXCUSE YOURSELF,

552
00:37:48,699 --> 00:37:51,636
WHIP IT OUT
AND WAKE UP MR. FLOPPY.

553
00:37:55,239 --> 00:37:58,209
DON'T TELL YOUR MOTHER,
BUT I THINK THE QUICKEST WAY
TO HEAVEN...

554
00:37:58,209 --> 00:38:02,413
IS WITH HALF A JAR
OF PETROLEUM JELLY
AND A CHAMOIS LEATHER GLOVE.

555
00:38:02,413 --> 00:38:06,751
FOR GOD SAKES, SON,
JUST LEAVE THESE GIRLS ALONE.

556
00:38:06,751 --> 00:38:09,687
JUST FOR THE TIME BEING,
OKAY? EH?

557
00:38:09,687 --> 00:38:11,605
YEAH.

558
00:38:11,605 --> 00:38:15,559
ALL RIGHT, SLUGGER?

559
00:38:15,559 --> 00:38:19,981
OH, AND, SON,
ONE MORE THING.

560
00:38:19,981 --> 00:38:24,068
LET'S KEEP THIS LITTLE TALK
JUST BETWEEN OURSELVES, OKAY?

561
00:38:24,068 --> 00:38:27,188
