SHE WOULDN'T UNDERSTAND.

562
00:38:27,188 --> 00:38:28,622
UH, DAD?

563
00:38:31,575 --> 00:38:33,077
YEAH.
OW!

564
00:38:51,495 --> 00:38:55,383
[ Toothbrush Scrubbing ]

565
00:38:55,383 --> 00:38:58,386
???? [ Soft Jazz ]

566
00:40:10,157 --> 00:40:13,861
[ Purring ]

567
00:40:13,861 --> 00:40:16,597
AL? I'M ALREADY LOTIONED.

568
00:40:17,014 --> 00:40:17,998
???? [ Record Scratches ]

569
00:40:23,454 --> 00:40:24,955
[ Sighs ]

570
00:40:26,941 --> 00:40:28,943
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

571
00:40:28,943 --> 00:40:30,945
I'M GONNA GO
BUFF THE PIG.

572
00:40:30,945 --> 00:40:32,947
OKAY, DEAR.

573
00:40:34,448 --> 00:40:37,885
