574
00:41:00,391 --> 00:41:02,393
[ Yelling ]

575
00:41:11,335 --> 00:41:14,839
???? [ Humming ]

576
00:41:14,839 --> 00:41:16,340
MORNING, HONEY.
HEY.

577
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:18,826
LOOKS LIKE SOMEBODY GOT UP
ON THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE BED.

578
00:41:18,826 --> 00:41:21,328
OH, YEAH.

579
00:41:21,328 --> 00:41:23,314
GOOD MORNING, YOU TWO.

580
00:41:23,314 --> 00:41:24,815
MOM, WHAT'S UP?

581
00:41:25,316 --> 00:41:28,736
WE'RE PUTTING ON SOME
SCENES FROM THE BIBLE
FOR THE CHURCH PRESCHOOL.

582
00:41:28,736 --> 00:41:31,238
I'M A STONING VICTIM.
PANCAKES?

583
00:41:31,238 --> 00:41:33,190
NO TIME FOR BREAKFAST
THIS MORNING, HONEY.

584
00:41:33,691 --> 00:41:36,177
BUT, AL, I MADE
THE HAPPY FACE PANCAKES.

585
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:39,613
YOU KNOW,
WITH THE CHOCOLATE CHIPS.

586
00:41:46,020 --> 00:41:48,022
YOU KIDS REMEMBER
EVERYTHING YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO SAY AND DO IN SCHOOL?

587
00:41:48,022 --> 00:41:49,023
YEAH, NO SWEAT.

588
00:41:51,025 --> 00:41:53,978
[ Door Closes ]

589
00:41:55,479 --> 00:41:56,931
YOU LOOK GREAT, MOM.

590
00:41:56,931 --> 00:42:00,367
I'M STONED.

591
00:42:08,342 --> 00:42:13,347
[ Amber ] SADLY,
ADAM WAS FORCED TO PRETEND
THAT HE REALLY LIKED GINGER.

592
00:42:13,347 --> 00:42:16,350
HE'S A REALLY GOOD ACTOR.

593
00:42:28,312 --> 00:42:31,315
IF YOU REALLY LOVED ME,
YOU'D BE CARRYING
MY BOOKS.

594
00:42:38,822 --> 00:42:41,325
EWW.
SO DO WE HAVE TO BE
FRIENDS WITH HER NOW?

595
00:42:46,130 --> 00:42:48,566
ADAM!
???? [ Record Scratches ]

596
00:42:52,052 --> 00:42:53,520
UH-OH.

597
00:42:53,520 --> 00:42:55,956
LOOK, I-- I NEED
TO TALK TO YOU, BABY.

598
00:42:56,457 --> 00:42:58,459
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WITH THIS HO-BAG?

599
00:42:58,459 --> 00:43:00,461
HEY!
EWW!

600
00:43:02,963 --> 00:43:05,966
JUST COME HERE.
WHERE ARE WE GOING?

601
00:43:13,857 --> 00:43:15,359
IF YOU WEREN'T
THE MOST POPULAR GUY
IN HIGH SCHOOL,

602
00:43:15,859 --> 00:43:17,861
I WOULD SO BE
BREAKING UP WITH YOU.

603
00:43:17,861 --> 00:43:20,364
BABY, WILL YOU JUST
LISTEN TO ME FOR ONE SECOND?

604
00:43:20,364 --> 00:43:23,367
GINGER AND I HAVE TO PRETEND
THAT WE'RE DATING AND IN LOVE.

605
00:43:23,367 --> 00:43:24,868
COME ON. YOU EXPECT ME
TO BELIEVE THAT?

606
00:43:25,369 --> 00:43:27,855
WHAT KIND OF MORON WOULD
TELL YOU TO DO THAT?
CHUCK DID.

607
00:43:27,855 --> 00:43:31,792
I'M SORRY.
WAS I TALKING TO YOU?
NO, I DON'T THINK I WAS.

608
00:43:31,792 --> 00:43:33,744
WELL, HE DID.
MY LAWYER SAID...

609
00:43:33,744 --> 00:43:35,696
THAT IF EVERYONE
THINKS THAT I'M INNOCENT,

610
00:43:35,696 --> 00:43:36,697
I COULD GET OFF.

611
00:43:37,197 --> 00:43:40,084
HAVEN'T YOU GOTTEN OFF
ENOUGH ALREADY?

612
00:43:40,084 --> 00:43:41,585
BABY, I LOVE YOU.

613
00:43:41,585 --> 00:43:44,088
THAT IS NOT THE PLAN.

614
00:43:44,088 --> 00:43:47,074
YOU MAKE MY HEART SING
WITH THE SOUND OF MUSIC.

615
00:43:47,074 --> 00:43:48,509
YEAH, I ALREADY HAVE
A BOYFRIEND.

616
00:43:49,009 --> 00:43:49,977
AND HE TREATS ME REAL GOOD.

617
00:43:49,977 --> 00:43:51,979
HOW NICE FOR YOU.
YOU CAN HAVE ADAM.

618
00:43:52,463 --> 00:43:53,897
THIS IS JUST SO
WE CAN GET A SETTLEMENT.

619
00:43:57,701 --> 00:43:59,119
SETTLEMENT?

620
00:43:59,119 --> 00:44:01,488
CHUCK SAID THAT IF WE
GET THROUGH THIS PART,

621
00:44:01,488 --> 00:44:05,909
WE'LL BE ABLE TO SUE
THE STATE OR THE PRESIDENT
OR SOMETHING AND GET CASH.

622
00:44:05,909 --> 00:44:06,827
HE DID.

623
00:44:08,646 --> 00:44:10,280
REALLY?

624
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:12,466
LIKE HOW MUCH ARE WE
TALKING ABOUT HERE?

625
00:44:12,933 --> 00:44:14,385
LIKE A WHOLE TRUCKLOAD.

626
00:44:14,385 --> 00:44:16,337
HMM.

627
00:44:18,989 --> 00:44:21,492
THIS WILL MAKE ME LOOK
REALLY, REALLY STUPID.

628
00:44:21,492 --> 00:44:23,977
