MAKE YOU LOOK STUPID?

629
00:44:23,977 --> 00:44:25,879
I DO!

630
00:44:26,380 --> 00:44:27,865
WHAT IF I GET CHUCK
TO PUT A SPIN ON THE STORY?

631
00:44:28,365 --> 00:44:31,518
WOULD THAT MAKE YOU
FEEL BETTER?

632
00:44:31,518 --> 00:44:35,689
HMM. WELL, HOW LONG
UNTIL WE GET THE MONEY?

633
00:44:36,190 --> 00:44:41,111
AS SOON AS ADAM GETS OFF
AND I HAVE MY BABY,
THEN I'M SO OUT OF HERE.

634
00:44:41,111 --> 00:44:44,565
BESIDES, JOHNNY ALREADY HAS
A TRAILER PICKED OUT
FOR THE BOTH OF US.

635
00:44:44,565 --> 00:44:48,419
AWW. THAT'S REALLY GREAT,
LITTLE WHATEVER
YOUR NAME IS,

636
00:44:48,919 --> 00:44:51,422
