AND WOULD YOU MIND
SHUTTING UP?

637
00:44:51,422 --> 00:44:52,923
BECAUSE I WASN'T
TALKING TO YOU!

638
00:44:52,923 --> 00:44:54,792
BITCH.

639
00:44:56,677 --> 00:44:59,146
WHAT DID YOU
JUST CALL ME?

640
00:44:59,146 --> 00:45:00,647
