641
00:45:05,302 --> 00:45:06,754
[ Girls Yelling ]

642
00:45:11,241 --> 00:45:14,628
[ Yelling Continues ]

643
00:45:25,456 --> 00:45:28,459
[ Amber ]
THE SKANKETTE HAD LANDED ADAM
IN SO MUCH TROUBLE.

644
00:45:28,459 --> 00:45:31,462
THE ONLY PLACE LEFT
FOR HIM TO GO...

645
