BECAUSE HE GOT LUCKY
WITH HIS GIRLFRIEND.

1283
01:22:25,006 --> 01:22:28,310
THEREFORE, MR. FISHER,
I AM SENTENCING YOU
TO TWO YEARS...

1284
01:22:28,310 --> 01:22:31,680
PROBATION.

1285
01:22:32,113 --> 01:22:35,850
AND AS FOR THAT REQUIREMENT
THAT YOU REGISTER
AS A SEXUAL PREDATOR,

1286
01:22:35,850 --> 01:22:38,403
IT'S REQUIRED
BY THE STATUTE,

1287
01:22:38,403 --> 01:22:42,090
SO I'M AFRAID
THAT MY HANDS ARE TIED.

1288
01:22:42,090 --> 01:22:43,758
BUT GOOD LUCK, ADAM.

1289
01:22:45,360 --> 01:22:49,681
I WANT TO THANK
THE COMMUNITY FOR
THEIR INCREDIBLE SUPPORT...

1290
01:22:50,181 --> 01:22:51,182
AND THAT JUDGE, TOO.

1291
01:22:51,182 --> 01:22:52,684
OKAY, I'M GONNA THROW IT
OVER TO ADAM HERE.

1292
01:22:53,184 --> 01:22:55,186
HE'S GOING TO TAKE
A FEW QUESTIONS BEFORE
I GIVE YOU ANY MORE DETAILS...

1293
01:22:55,687 --> 01:22:58,189
ABOUT MY BOOK SIGNING TOUR.
[ Reporters Yelling ]

1294
01:22:58,189 --> 01:23:01,693
HOW DOES IT FEEL TO HAVE TO
REGISTER AS A SEXUAL PREDATOR
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE?

1295
01:23:02,193 --> 01:23:03,695
WELL, IT KINDA SUCKS.

1296
01:23:03,695 --> 01:23:06,197
I MEAN, NOW I WON'T BE ABLE
TO COACH KIDS' BASEBALL...

1297
01:23:06,197 --> 01:23:09,701
OR BUY A GUN
OR BE THE PRESIDENT
OF THE UNITED STATES.

1298
01:23:09,701 --> 01:23:11,703
HOW DO YOU AND GINGER
PLAN TO CELEBRATE
YOUR FREEDOM...

1299
01:23:11,703 --> 01:23:14,205
AND WHEN DO YOU
PLAN ON GETTING MARRIED?

1300
01:23:14,205 --> 01:23:17,208
WELL, GINGER AND I
KIND OF BROKE UP.

1301
01:23:20,211 --> 01:23:23,715
THAT'S ALL THE TIME
THAT HE HAS FOR--
FOR YOU GUYS RIGHT NOW,

1302
01:23:23,715 --> 01:23:28,219
BUT I GOT LOTS OF TIME,
SO, UH, LET'S GET IT ON.

1303
01:23:28,219 --> 01:23:31,723
OKAY, SO THE TITLE OF MY BOOK
ISUNLAWFUL ENTRY:
THE ADAM FISHER STORY.

1304
01:23:31,723 --> 01:23:34,225
IF ORDER ONE RIGHT NOW,
YOU'LL GET A SPECIAL COPY
OF MY WORKOUT VIDEO...

1305
01:23:34,225 --> 01:23:36,661
HOW TO GET GREAT ABS
IN JUST THREE HEARINGS.

1306
01:23:37,162 --> 01:23:38,163
[ Amber ]
WITH THE WHOLE MESS BEHIND US,

1307
01:23:38,663 --> 01:23:40,165
ADAM AND I CAN GET
OUR LIVES BACK...

1308
01:23:40,165 --> 01:23:42,667
AND ENJOY
EVEN DEEPER TRUE LOVE.

1309
01:23:42,667 --> 01:23:47,172
SEE, SWEETIE, I WAS THINKING
MAYBE WE COULD GO BACK
TO MY PLACE...

1310
01:23:47,172 --> 01:23:49,174
AND CELEBRATE YOUR VICTORY.

1311
01:23:49,174 --> 01:23:52,677
JEEZ, I DON'T KNOW.
I'VE KINDA BEEN
THINKING, TOO.

1312
01:23:52,677 --> 01:23:55,180
I'LL HAVE YOUR BABY! I'M 16!

1313
01:23:55,180 --> 01:23:57,682
I LOVE YOU, ADAM!
I WANNA HAVE YOUR BABY!

1314
01:23:57,682 --> 01:24:00,185
MARRY ME, ADAM,
I LOVE YOU!

1315
01:24:00,185 --> 01:24:03,188
WHAT DO YOU SORT OF THINK
ABOUT SEEING OTHER PEOPLE?

1316
01:24:05,190 --> 01:24:08,193
[ Girls Screaming ]

1317
01:24:08,193 --> 01:24:10,195
[ Amber ]
SOMEWHERE DEEP DOWN,

1318
01:24:10,195 --> 01:24:12,197
I KNOW HE REALLY
COULDN'T MEAN THAT.

1319
01:24:12,197 --> 01:24:14,699
HE WAS JUST IN SHOCK
FROM THE TRIAL.

1320
01:24:14,699 --> 01:24:16,701
HE LOVES ME TOO MUCH
TO SEE OTHER PEOPLE.

1321
01:24:17,202 --> 01:24:19,687
[ Screaming ]
I JUST HAD TO REMIND HIM.

1322
01:24:23,041 --> 01:24:25,510
?? I DON'T BELIEVE
  WHAT HE SAID ??

1323
01:24:25,510 --> 01:24:27,512
?? I CAN GO ANYWHERE ??

1324
01:24:27,512 --> 01:24:29,514
?? I CAN HOLD MY HEAD UP ??

1325
01:24:30,014 --> 01:24:32,016
?? I CAN BREATHE IN THE AIR ??

1326
01:24:32,016 --> 01:24:34,519
?? I'M NOT OFFICIALLY DEAD ??

1327
01:24:34,519 --> 01:24:36,521
?? I STILL HAVE A HEART ??

1328
01:24:36,521 --> 01:24:39,023
?? NOT OFFICIALLY DEAD, YEAH ??

1329
01:24:39,023 --> 01:24:41,860
?? I STILL HAVE A HEART ??

1330
01:24:42,360 --> 01:24:43,862
[ Amber ]
I MAY HAVE
GONE ABOUT IT BADLY,

1331
01:24:44,362 --> 01:24:48,299
BUT WHAT'S IMPORTANT
IN THE END IS THAT WE
LEARN FROM OUR MISTAKES...

1332
01:24:48,299 --> 01:24:50,301
AND GROW AS INDIVIDUALS.

1333
01:24:50,301 --> 01:24:53,805
?
?? I REMEMBER THE TIMES YOU'D
  RIDE YOUR BIKE PAST MY HOUSE ?

1334
01:24:53,805 --> 01:24:55,774
?? I WANNA KNOW YOU SO BAD ??

1335
01:24:56,274 --> 01:24:58,276
?? KNOW YOU INSIDE AND OUT ??

1336
01:24:58,276 --> 01:25:00,779
?? YOU'RE OFFICIALLY DEAD ??

1337
01:25:00,779 --> 01:25:02,280
?? YOU DON'T HAVE A HEART ????

1338
01:25:02,280 --> 01:25:05,416
???? [ Piano ]

1339
01:25:27,522 --> 01:25:30,525
AH! OOH!

1340
01:25:30,525 --> 01:25:32,527
MY!

1341
01:25:33,745 --> 01:25:35,396
[ Amber ]
ANYHOW, YOU'RE
PROBABLY WONDERING...

1342
01:25:35,396 --> 01:25:37,799
WHAT HAPPENED TO EVERYONE
AFTER THE TRIAL.

1343
01:25:37,799 --> 01:25:41,653
[ Ginger Screaming ]

1344
01:25:42,153 --> 01:25:44,656
[ Grunting ]

1345
01:25:45,140 --> 01:25:46,741
[ Baby Crying ]

1346
01:25:47,142 --> 01:25:50,094
[ Amber ]
AFTER A COUNTY RECORD
OF 98 HOURS OF LABOR,

1347
01:25:50,094 --> 01:25:52,597
GINGER PRODUCED A BABY GIRL,

1348
01:25:52,597 --> 01:25:55,600
THUS PROVING THAT
SHE'S NOT ALWAYS EASY.

1349
01:25:57,602 --> 01:25:59,604
GINGER,
CAN I TOUCH IT?

1350
01:25:59,604 --> 01:26:01,105
NO WAY!
HUSH, JOHNNY!

1351
01:26:01,606 --> 01:26:04,609
GINGER'S MINE NOW,
ASS WIPE!
HE MEANS THE BABY.

1352
01:26:04,609 --> 01:26:06,611
[ Crying ]

1353
01:26:07,111 --> 01:26:09,113
SHH SHH SHH!
HERE, BABY, COME HERE.

1354
01:26:09,113 --> 01:26:12,116
GIVE IT TO JOHNNY.
GIVE IT TO JOHNNY.

1355
01:26:12,116 --> 01:26:14,619
THERE YOU GO.

1356
01:26:14,619 --> 01:26:16,120
WHAT'S ITS NAME?

1357
01:26:16,120 --> 01:26:19,557
WE DECIDED TO NAME HER "T-BONE"
AFTER JOHNNY'S CELLMATE.

1358
01:26:19,557 --> 01:26:21,059
[ Crying Continues ]
OH, WAIT, WHAT'D I DO?

1359
01:26:21,059 --> 01:26:26,531
HERE, HERE. YOU'RE JUST
HOLDING HER WRONG.

1360
01:26:27,015 --> 01:26:29,083
[ Ginger ]
JOHNNY KNOWS ALL ABOUT BABIES.

1361
01:26:29,083 --> 01:26:31,452
HIS SISTER HAD A COUPLE
BACK IN JUNIOR HIGH,

1362
01:26:31,452 --> 01:26:33,454
AND HE HELPED
TAKE CARE OF THEM.
PUT YOUR HAND HERE.

1363
01:26:33,955 --> 01:26:37,458
HE'S GONNA BE A GREAT DADDY.
THERE YOU GO.

1364
01:26:37,458 --> 01:26:39,961
THERE YOU GO.
[ Laughs ]

1365
01:26:39,961 --> 01:26:42,463
YEAH. YEAH.

1366
01:26:42,463 --> 01:26:44,732
[ Amber ]
ALTHOUGH LYDIA
LOST THE ELECTION,

1367
01:26:44,732 --> 01:26:48,937
HER NEWLY FOUND CELEBRITY
LANDED HER A TALK SHOW ON CNBC,

1368
01:26:49,337 --> 01:26:51,339
WHICH WAS CANCELED
AFTER SIX SHOWS.

1369
01:26:51,739 --> 01:26:55,476
SHE FOUND A BETTER OUTLET
FOR HER TALENTS ON
THE HOME BUYING CHANNEL.

1370
01:26:55,476 --> 01:26:57,545
DON'T FORGET TO ORDER
THIS LIMITED EDITION...

1371
01:26:57,946 --> 01:26:59,397
ADAM AND GINGER
DINNER PLATE SET.

1372
01:26:59,898 --> 01:27:02,183
THAT'S RIGHT, LYDIA.
THIS IS VERY INTERESTING.

1373
01:27:02,183 --> 01:27:03,785
THE PAINTING THAT
YOU'RE LOOKING AT HERE...

1374
01:27:03,785 --> 01:27:06,187
IS BAKED RIGHT IN
SO IT WON'T CHIP OR FADE.

1375
01:27:06,588 --> 01:27:08,273
[ Lydia ]
MM-HMM. THESE ARE A MUST-HAVE.

1376
01:27:08,273 --> 01:27:11,109
AN EXCELLENT BARGAIN,
AND DISHWASHER-SAFE
AS WELL.

1377
01:27:11,109 --> 01:27:15,730
WE HARDLY HAVE ANY LEFT,
SO GET ON THAT PHONE
AND CALL 555-LONG.

1378
01:27:15,730 --> 01:27:17,732
I HAVE SOME OF THESE
AT HOME, CHUCK.

1379
01:27:20,585 --> 01:27:23,087
[ Amber ]
ADAM DID DROP OUT OF SCHOOL
BEFORE GRADUATION,

1380
01:27:23,087 --> 01:27:25,590
AND ONCE AGAIN FOUND HIMSELF
AT THE LITTLE CHICKEN.

1381
01:27:26,090 --> 01:27:27,592
HE HAD A FEW LEGAL BILLS.

1382
01:27:27,592 --> 01:27:31,596
AND LET'S FACE IT--
SCHOOL WAS JUST NEVER HIS THING.

1383
01:27:34,599 --> 01:27:36,584
[ Whistling ]
[ Amber ]
IT WASN'T LONG...

1384
01:27:36,584 --> 01:27:39,587
BEFORE ANOTHER BABY
GOT STUCK IN A PIPE SOMEWHERE--

1385
01:27:39,587 --> 01:27:41,089
ARKANSAS, I THINK--

1386
01:27:41,089 --> 01:27:44,092
SO THE PRESS ESCAPED
OUR SMALL, PICTURESQUE TOWN,

1387
01:27:44,092 --> 01:27:47,595
AND ADAM'S PARENTS QUICKLY
FOUND THEMSELVES BACK TO NORMAL.

1388
01:27:47,595 --> 01:27:50,098
AL?

1389
01:27:50,098 --> 01:27:52,600
IT'S BLUE.

1390
01:27:55,103 --> 01:27:57,605
[ Amber ]
WELL, ALMOST.

1391
01:28:00,608 --> 01:28:02,110
OH, MY.

1392
01:28:02,110 --> 01:28:05,697
AS FOR ME,

1393
01:28:05,697 --> 01:28:08,700
WELL, I'M DOING JUST FINE.

1394
01:28:11,636 --> 01:28:13,638
AFTER THE LITTLE INCIDENT
WITH ADAM'S CAR,

1395
01:28:14,138 --> 01:28:18,643
I AGREED TO MAKE A FEW SPEECHES
AT LOCAL JUNIOR HIGH SCHOOLS
ON THE DANGERS OF TEEN SEX.

1396
01:28:19,143 --> 01:28:21,646
I'M A VERY GIVING PERSON.

1397
01:28:21,646 --> 01:28:23,648
I AM.

1398
01:28:25,149 --> 01:28:26,651
[ Amber Narrating ]
AFTER ALL WE WENT THROUGH,

1399
01:28:26,651 --> 01:28:31,155
WE PATCHED THINGS UP
AND EMERGED CLOSER THAN EVER.

1400
01:28:31,656 --> 01:28:33,157
IT TOOK A LITTLE NUDGING
ON MY PART,

1401
01:28:33,157 --> 01:28:36,160
BUT EVENTUALLY I GOT ADAM
TO POP THE QUESTION.

1402
01:28:36,160 --> 01:28:38,162
HAPPIEST DAY OF MY LIFE.

1403
01:28:53,895 --> 01:28:56,931
[ Amber ]
ADAM STILL HAD
SOME GROWING UP TO DO,

1404
01:28:56,931 --> 01:28:59,434
BUT I'M LEARNING TO BE PATIENT.

1405
01:28:59,934 --> 01:29:03,905
WE'RE GOING TO BE TOGETHER
FOR A LONG,

1406
01:29:03,905 --> 01:29:06,824
LONG TIME.

1407
01:29:06,824 --> 01:29:07,825
ADAM!

1408
01:29:07,825 --> 01:29:12,263
SO YOU SEE,
STORIES DO HAVE HAPPY ENDINGS.

1409
01:29:12,263 --> 01:29:14,699
NO, REALLY! THEY DO!

1410
01:29:18,202 --> 01:29:20,204
HERE, BABE.

1411
01:29:20,204 --> 01:29:22,206
THANKS, BABE.

1412
01:29:23,708 --> 01:29:26,210
LET ME JUST GET THESE
HANDLEBARS FOR YOU.

1413
01:29:32,717 --> 01:29:34,719
?? I GUESS WE'VE HAD OUR FUN ??

1414
01:29:35,219 --> 01:29:37,188
?? BUT IT SEEMS THE FUN
  IS OVER NOW ??

1415
01:29:37,188 --> 01:29:39,690
?? AND THAT'S ALL RIGHT ??

1416
01:29:39,690 --> 01:29:42,193
?? IT'S ALL RIGHT ??

1417
01:29:57,024 --> 01:30:00,411
I CALLED YOU A BITCH,
WHICH YOU MOST DEFINITELY ARE!

1418
01:30:01,779 --> 01:30:04,782
[ Giggling ]

1419
01:30:10,671 --> 01:30:14,525
HOW DO YOU-- HOW--
HOW DO YOU FEEL?

1420
01:30:15,026 --> 01:30:18,362
OTHER THAN MORNING SICKNESS
AND OCCASIONAL CONSTIPATION--

1421
01:30:18,362 --> 01:30:21,849
I KNOW ALL ABOUT THAT,
BUT MENTALLY.

1422
01:30:21,849 --> 01:30:23,701
HELLO?

1423
01:30:38,933 --> 01:30:41,352
[ Judge ]
MR. FISHER,
WOULD YOU BE SO KIND?

1424
01:30:41,352 --> 01:30:42,854
YES, SIR.

1425
01:30:44,272 --> 01:30:47,158
- CUT!
- SHE LOVES HER CORN.

1426
01:30:47,658 --> 01:30:50,661
WHAT HAND ARE YOU COUNTING ON?
SECOND TIME.

1427
01:30:50,661 --> 01:30:52,663
THIRD TIME.
SHUT UP.

1428
01:30:54,065 --> 01:30:57,502
WHERE YOU GOING?

1429
01:30:58,002 --> 01:31:00,004
I'M GONNA DO THE DANCE
WITH THE JUG-EARED MAN.

1430
01:31:00,004 --> 01:31:01,472
FORGOT TO FLOSS.

1431
01:31:01,973 --> 01:31:03,941
I'M GONNA BEAT OFF.

1432
01:31:03,941 --> 01:31:05,943
THAT'S NICE, DEAR.

1433
01:31:21,242 --> 01:31:24,462
OKAY, I OBJECT, YOUR HONOR!
HE'S LEADING HIMSELF!

1434
01:31:24,462 --> 01:31:27,965
I'M SORRY, I--
WE NEED TO STOP
FOR A SECOND.

1435
01:31:27,965 --> 01:31:30,368
ALL RIGHT, I'M LACTATING
AND I'M LEAKING RIGHT NOW.

1436
01:31:30,368 --> 01:31:33,337
PARTY ANIMAL.

1437
01:31:33,337 --> 01:31:35,523
[ Judge ]
YOU'RE ASKING
THE QUESTION.

1438
01:31:36,007 --> 01:31:39,443
THANK YOU,
YOUR HONOR.
I KNOW.

1439
01:31:39,927 --> 01:31:43,397
AND ALL HE GOT WAS TO PICK OUT--
ALL HE HAD TO DO WAS
PICK UP TRASH.

1440
01:31:44,899 --> 01:31:46,868
LOOK, EITHER LOVE
THE LITTLE TRAMP,

1441
01:31:46,868 --> 01:31:49,086
OR YOU'RE GONNA BE
GETTING SOME TOUGH LOVE...

1442
01:31:49,086 --> 01:31:51,239
FROM YOUR CELLMATE
UP AT THE STATE PEN.

1443
01:31:51,739 --> 01:31:54,992
SOAP ON A ROPE
SO YOU CAN GET IT BACK.
GOT IT?

1444
01:32:09,824 --> 01:32:14,078
WHAT THE HECK
YOU TALKING ABOUT?
IT'S A HYGIENE THING, HONEY.

1445
01:32:16,430 --> 01:32:19,934
UH, IT'S
A WORKOUT METAPHOR.

1446
01:32:19,934 --> 01:32:22,803
[ No Audible Dialogue ]

1447
01:32:25,306 --> 01:32:27,241
HI.

1448
01:32:49,931 --> 01:32:52,300
I WANNA TRY OUT
MY NEW WATER PIK.

1449
01:32:52,300 --> 01:32:53,968
YOU'RE MY HONOR.
CALL ME YOUR HONOR.

1450
01:32:53,968 --> 01:32:58,339
[ Adam ]
THERE'S ULTIMATE FIGHTING
ON PAY-PER-VIEW TONIGHT.

1451
01:32:58,339 --> 01:33:00,174
OH. OH, YEAH?

1452
01:33:00,675 --> 01:33:02,026
YOU ANYBODY'S BITCH YET?

1453
01:33:02,026 --> 01:33:03,844
- WHAT?
- SOUND GOOD?

1454
01:33:06,397 --> 01:33:08,015
- COOL.
- NO PROBLEM.

1455
01:33:28,102 --> 01:33:30,955
W-WE CAN'T DO IT
ANYMORE?

1456
01:33:30,955 --> 01:33:33,541
I CAN'T DO IT ANYMORE?

1457
01:33:35,409 --> 01:33:36,911
WE CAN'T DO IT
ANYMORE?

1458
01:33:36,911 --> 01:33:37,828
WELL, FOLKS--

1459
01:33:38,312 --> 01:33:40,281
WAS YOUR BED GOOD, HONEY?

1460
01:33:41,716 --> 01:33:43,217
HAVE YOU BEEN
BONING HER AGAIN?

1461
01:33:43,217 --> 01:33:45,720
OH, NO.

1462
01:33:47,388 --> 01:33:49,507
[ Giggling ]

